OL,6,Fare reportedly seeking damages from
OL,7,Fthe Premier League as they look to
OL,8,Fthrow out the league's "unlawful"
OL,9,Frules, which have caused a major
OL,10,Fdivide among Premier League clubs.
OL,12,FAssociated Party Transaction (APT)
OL,13,Frules were introduced in December 2021
OL,14,Ffollowing the Saudi takeover of , and
OL,15,Fare designed to stop clubs inflating
OL,16,Fcommercial deals with companies linked
OL,17,Fto their owners.
