OL,3,CManchester City 'launch legal action
OL,4,Cagainst Premier League'
OL,6,FThey were brought in in an effort to
OL,7,Fmaintain the competitiveness of the
OL,8,FPremier League, following an increase
OL,9,Fin state ownership of the clubs.
OL,11,FThe Times is reporting in a two-week
OL,12,Fprivate arbitration hearing, due to
OL,13,Fstart on Monday 10 June, City will
OL,14,Fattempt to end those APT rules as the
OL,15,Fclub has argued they are against
OL,16,Fcompetition law.
OL,18,FIt is claimed City also say the rules
OL,19,Fare discriminatory to clubs with ties
OL,20,Fto the Gulf region and clubs that are
OL,21,Fbased outside of London.
