OL,3,CManchester City 'launch legal action
OL,4,Cagainst Premier League'
OL,6,FAs well as looking to end the rules,
OL,7,Fthe club is also said to be seeking
OL,8,Fdamages for money it has not been able
OL,9,Fto make since the rules were brought
OL,10,Fin.
OL,12,FIf City are successful, it would
OL,13,Fenable the richest clubs to value
OL,14,Ftheir sponsorship deals without them
OL,15,Fbeing independently assessed, which
OL,16,Fcould potentially massively boost
OL,17,Ftheir transfer funds.
